{"tid":1039590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"回撥房屋儲備金「掩飾赤字」？　陳茂波：「明搶阿吹阿？」","createTime":"2019-02-27T13:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T13:46:04.000Z","uid":219681,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"914f8802b84b63e0262f826207bb664119d4140f","tid":1039590,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"新一份《財政預算案》宣布將2014年設立、現已滾存至824億元的房屋儲備金，分4年回撥至財政儲備。陳茂波下午出席記者會被問及是否為「掩飾赤字」，他回應時指出，「計及回撥了的212億元，我們（政府）才有170多億盈餘，所以是赤字預算案」。他又指，何時將房屋儲備金納入，「永遠都沒有最佳時機」，認為做法不是「結構上的大變化」。<br />\n<br />\n上屆政府在2014年設立房屋儲備金，以資助公營房屋發展計劃，金額不計入政府帳目，也不是財政儲備的一部分。陳茂波今早在立法會表示，計及2019/20年度從房屋儲備金回撥的212億元後，預計該年度錄得168億元的綜合盈餘。<br />\n<br />\n包括2019/20年度，政府會將824億元的房屋儲備金分4年回撥，並納入財政儲備（即至2022/23年度），而根據政府今日公布的中期預測，政府會分別在2020/21年度至2022/23年度，錄得276億、49億元和55億元的綜合盈餘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190227/s00001/1551259367782/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%9B%9E%E6%92%A5%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99%E9%87%91%E3%80%8C%E6%8E%A9%E9%A3%BE%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E3%80%8D-%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E6%98%AF%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551259367782%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2582%2599%25E9%2587%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258E%25A9%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E3%2580%258D-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=d80cc774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551259367782%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2582%2599%25E9%2587%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258E%25A9%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E3%2580%258D-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588&h=f0e8c4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190227/s00001/1551259367782/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%9B%9E%E6%92%A5%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99%E9%87%91%E3%80%8C%E6%8E%A9%E9%A3%BE%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E3%80%8D-%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E6%98%AF%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n我Hi 你條肥波，好嬲阿<br />\n阿叔儲嘅錢俾你敗曬，而家仲要搶錢填數<br />\n我咒你祖宗十八代"},{"pid":"9ef603fecc15614ab498c8cb74fce1d0f1acac7f","tid":1039590,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"😡😡😡😡😡"},{"pid":"9322ada76623618dfcc98edf82d0b7c8ae2b2fcc","tid":1039590,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"咒到你現眼報😡"},{"pid":"05fe24bae70215abd54f64a494e4d9fcbabfadb2","tid":1039590,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"劏房賺咁多，係時候嘔返出黎"},{"pid":"bcc179ad0c661e063f111f5106e8fc9115ce8701","tid":1039590,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"是但啦，份嘢都未必係finalized<br />\n之前先玩過彈弓手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n垃圾波，趁地淋啦"}]}